 Wednesday Night on Sky One!

Just letting everyone know that this wednesday on Sky One we have a double header of Stargate Episodes @ 8PM!

The Warrior - Braveheart ala Stargate. A young and charasmatic Jaffa decides to try and persuade his people to rise up against The Goa'uld.

Menace - Ah, those little Lego creatures, The Replicators retrun to us once again when SG-1 find a world controlled by The Replicators (A.K.A. - Lego Land!) and a young Girl who may be the ket to the Salvation of the Asgard. But she won't be, because it would mean the end of The Goa'uld as well and then the end of the TV Show.
